                            <p class="lg:mt-4 font-medium tracking-normal text-gray-500 line-clamp-3">The word photography means 'drawing with light,' which derives from the Greek photo, meaning light, and graph, meaning to draw. Photography is the process of recording an image â€“ a photograph â€“ on light-sensitive film or, in the case of digital Photography, via a digital electronic or magnetic memory.</p>
